quran[7{c,v,t}:
29,24,to unn ki qoum ke log jawab mein bolay to yeh bolay ke ussay maar daalo ya jala do. magar khuda ne unn ko aag ( ki soozish ) se bchalya. jo log imaan rakhtay hain unn ke liye is mein nishanain hain
29,25,aur ibrahim ne kaha ke tum jo khuda ko chore kar buton ko le baithy ho to duniya ki zindagi mein baahum dosti ke liye ( magar ) phir qayamat ke din tum aik dosray ( ki dosti ) se inkaar kar do ge aur aik dosray par laanat bhaijho ge aur tumhara thikana dozakh hoga aur koi tumhara madadgaar nah hoga
29,26,pas unn par ( aik ) Loot imaan laaye aur ( ibrahim ) kehnay lagey ke mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf hijrat karne wala hon. bay shak woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
29,27,aur hum ne unn ko ashq aur Yaqoob bakhshay aur unn ki aulaad mein paigambri aur kitaab ( muqarrar ) kar di aur un ko duniya mein bhi unn ka sila inayatkiya aur woh akhirat mein bhi naik logon mein hon ge
29,28,aur Loot ( ko yaad karo ) jab onhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum ( ajab ) be hiyai ke murtakib hotay ho. tum se pehlay ahal aalam mein se kisi ne aisa kaam nahikiya
29,29,tum kyun ( lazzat ke iraday se ) london ki taraf ma-il hotay aur ( musafiron ki ) rehzani karte ho aur apni mjlson mein napasandeedah kaam karte ho. to unn ki qoum ke log jawab mein bolay to yeh bolay ke agar tum sachey ho to hum par azaab le aao
29,30,Loot ne kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar un mufsid logon ke muqablay mein mujhe nusrat inayat farma
